request.description:
**Description:**
Fetches a list of all files stored in the authenticated user's Google Drive.

**Headers:**

```json
{
  "Authorization": "Bearer <your_access_token>"
}
```

**Response (Success - 200 OK):**

```json
{
  "files": [
    {
      "id": "1X2Y3Z4ABC",
      "name": "example.pdf"
    },
    {
      "id": "4X5Y6Z7DEF",
      "name": "photo.png"
    }
  ]
}
```

**Response (Error - 400 Bad Request):**

```json
{
  "error": "Google Drive not linked"
}
```
